'''''Star Wars Weekly'' 68''' is the sixty-eighth issue of the ''[[Star Wars Weekly]]'' series of comic reprints, published on [[June 13]], [[1979]].

==Contents==
*[[Star Wars (1977) 29|''Star Wars'' (1977) 29]] {{C|Part 2}}
*"The power of Warlock Part 1: Here dwells the Star Thief!"
*"Micronauts Part 9: The macabre Man-Thing!"
*"Tales of the Watcher: What if World War II had been fought in Outer Space? Part 3: Attack from the stars!"

